+/**
+ * viortc_alarms_supported() - Whether device and driver support alarms.
+ * @vdev: virtio device
+ *
+ * NB: Device and driver may not support alarms for the same clocks.
+ *
+ * Context: Any context.
+ * Return: True if both device and driver can support alarms.
